Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直被监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫老胡和兰芳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道又失踪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一不注意就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又倒在路边的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳根清净了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家 有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}战友的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 来探望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大佐给的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 抽烟的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 赢过一回吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这个游戏太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 半夜的话可以去砍人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 至少把霍克爱大姐带来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回头和大姐说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要监视他到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们卷进这么危险的任务 真是对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军务方面不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你是因病请假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果被一般市民或我们的军队相关人员发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想简单了事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有前途一片光明的话题？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交上女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家遇见麻烦的时候 她对我很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 超好的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把那个女的砍了会不会很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是饿倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 从清国来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么从那大老远的地方跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你的入国许可证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非法入国者要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒在路边了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对饿倒在路边了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们就先去军部露个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就先去休斯家打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点看看克蕾西亚和艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我们马上就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 过会见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 休斯中佐有没有替我们收集贤者之石的情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被大总统禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把我们入手的情报告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐应该在军法会议所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着那边的钥匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 是三号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用过后就这么放着没收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我只是去拿需要的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻去收拾 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我等会来拿 麻烦你快点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离军队会议没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 也许是我多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还是不要太逞强多休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是马斯坦古大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好 佛卡大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 为什么大佐会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书库也开着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 其实那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是被大佐强行要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当没看见好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 大佐在调查什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道详细情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐问我有没有第五研究所的相关资料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 休斯准将的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是准将介绍我到这里工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有一堆工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 谢丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是瘦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南边遇上了点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到爱力克兄弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是去见达普利斯的师傅 偶然碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他们休斯已经去世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所和贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头的材料是活生生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙习惯管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插手爱力克兄弟在调查的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了不应该知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和自身的事件有关导致休斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两兄弟知道的话 心灵会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你调查得真彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定隔墙有耳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克爱中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉在的话 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大佐会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月开始我转到中央工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你今天干什么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微收集一下情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外想去和休斯中佐打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回乡下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着老婆和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想见他一面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别因为太过于心急 而做鲁莽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在这种时候把他们当孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那对兄弟来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进的路障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是越少越好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们总有一天会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没资格说阿姆斯壮少佐是老好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一句老好人就能解决的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点通知温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经去休斯家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么急？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了休斯中佐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一堆话想和他说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少想和他说声再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没有收到通知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 全军都给他送行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还挺人性化的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 也许你们已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他晋升两级 不是中佐 是准将了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晋升两级？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回乡下了却能晋升两级？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 为什么中佐会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯准将在爱德华出院后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被不明人物杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人还没被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把他卷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来中央都市的话 记得来打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯穿着铠甲没法吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还没决定住处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受责备的人只有我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是哥哥一个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们两个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然决定了无论发生什么事都要取回身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人为此而死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿放弃取回身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要对克蕾西亚夫人说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉也来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫知道了贤者之石的一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的死 是犯人警告你们不要再继续调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这完全是我们招来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救人而死 真像那个人的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前就是个爱管闲事爱操心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是帮了人家损了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我觉得他从来没有后悔过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在临死之时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说放弃之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的死就会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使贤者之石不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还有别的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蕾西亚夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用自己可以接受的方式前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂马上要关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃的话 身体会吃不消的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果派？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后 我练习了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己说出来像是自夸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比不上克蕾西亚夫人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想让休斯先生尝尝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐在调查休斯的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住什么线索了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了方便监视 才把他调到了中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让他乖乖待着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是重要的人柱候补
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你男朋友那里打听不出什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道他是天然呆还是老练
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去收集下情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吃完了不收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 拉斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要火焰之大佐安分下来就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试试另一个方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么计策？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于吵闹的狗 要给它点食物才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宪兵队司令部的 亨利·达古拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说明一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怀疑你杀害了马斯·休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会听你的辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉否认罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集这个人的相关资料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要隐秘行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 把这个花包一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索拉莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你 约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说些有趣的故事给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替罪羔羊被仇恨之火焰所焚烧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年受憎恶与后悔的侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人把手伸向了黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17话 冰冷的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如同在看不见的手上跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:06.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:12.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:30.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:36.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:43.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:59.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:14.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:19.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:33.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:44.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:08.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:16.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:22.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:27.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:32.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:44.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:48.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:52.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:56.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远

